穆德在《第六次大灭绝：命运之爱》中就像耶稣，科学家把他放在类似十字架的手术台上，在他身上实验，评论认为这场戏可比[[耶穌被釘十字架|耶穌被釘十字架]]。他头上还有金属环，就像耶稣的[[荆棘冠|荆棘冠]]。<ref name="Donaldson-2011" />{{rp|186, 209}}唐纳森认为，癌人在剧中建议穆德自保，呼应耶稣被绑上十字架时旁观者的劝说。她还进一步指出，穆德对外星病毒感染免疫，所以能成为人类的“救世主”，与基督徒眼中的人类救世主耶稣异曲同工。<ref name="Donaldson-2011" />{{rp|186}}

唐纳森的文章《穆德的最后诱惑》称，卡赞扎基斯小说中的耶稣“代表人类面临的终极挑战：在尘世局限中发扬神的一面”<ref name="Donaldson-2007" />{{rp|3}}。依此角度而言，耶稣在卡赞扎基斯小说中代表“绝对的人性”，代表“灵与肉之间的苦苦挣扎”<ref name="Donaldson-2007" />{{rp|23}}。癌人以梦想中的完美新生引诱穆德，后者必须克制诱惑、放弃梦中人生，勇于接受阻止外星人侵略的命运<ref name="Donaldson-2007" />{{rp|23}}。剧中多个人物的作用与小说角色类似，福雷就像卡赞扎基斯笔下[[抹大拉的馬利亞|抹大拉的馬利亞]]，两人都起阻挠英雄完成使命的作用<ref name="Donaldson-2007" />{{rp|17–18}}。斯嘉丽就像小说中的[[加略人猶大|加略人猶大]]，将恍惚中的英雄唤醒<ref name="Donaldson-2007" />{{rp|19}}。

麦克尔温认为，《第六次大灭绝：命运之爱》代表《{{lang|en|X}}档案》终于开始“将科学、宗教信仰和[[形上学|形而上学]]结合”<ref name="McIlwain-2005" />{{rp|151}}。斯嘉丽在本集抛开个人经验和推理挽救穆德的生命，相比之下，她在全剧绝大多数分集都是理智当头，不相信有超自然现象，觉得都有某种科学解释<ref name="McIlwain-2005" />{{rp|152}}<ref name="Donaldson-2011" />{{rp|5}}。她还在这集发现外星飞船碎片，推断外星人拥有“历史上所有问题的答案”<ref name="McIlwain-2005" />{{rp|152}}。穆德能够接受过于奇妙并超出科学解释的现象，愿意投身其中寻找真相，而且拥有解开谜团所必需的能力——对外星病毒免疫<ref name="McIlwain-2005" />{{rp|152}}。剧中探究的还有癌人的道德观念和他与邪恶的紧密联系。{{lang|en|Space.com}}网站的肯尼斯·西尔伯指出，癌人以花言巧语引诱穆德足以证明他是非常危险的敌人，就像[[撒旦崇拜|撒旦]]一样善于权术、操纵人心<ref name="space">{{cite news | last = Silber | first = Kenneth | title = The X-Files 'The Sixth Extinction (Amor Fati)' | url = http://space.com/sciencefiction/tv/xfiles_702_991115.html | work = Space.com | publisher = TechMediaNetwork | date = 2000-06-02 | accessdate = 2010-10-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101016011601/https://www.space.com/sciencefiction/tv/xfiles_702_991115.html | archivedate = 2010-10-16}}</ref>。蒂莫西·邓恩和约瑟夫·弗伊也在《癌人的道德沉思》一文指出，癌人本集中的恶行与他在辛迪加的任务无关，表明他是真正全身心投入的恶人<ref name="evil">{{cite book | last1 = Dunn | first1 = Timothy | last2 = Foy | first2 = Joseph | editor-last = Kowalski | editor-first = Dean | chapter = Moral Musings on a Cigarette Smoking Man | title = The Philosophy of The X-Files | publisher = University Press of Kentucky | year = 2007 | isbn = 9780813192277 | pages = 149–150}}</ref>。两人援引剧中台词“难道你不是在等我长出吸血鬼的獠牙来吗？”，证明癌人完全清楚自己的作为是多少罪恶，但他根本不在乎<ref name="evil" />。

== 播映和评价 ==
《第六次大灭绝：命运之爱》于1999年11月14日[[福斯廣播公司|福克斯电视网]]在美国首播，再于2000年3月26日经[[天空第一台|天空第一台]]首度向英国播映<ref name="DVD" />。节目在美国共吸引1615万户观众收看<ref name="Shapiro-2000" />{{rp|281}}，在这周所有电视联播网电视剧分集中排第27<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Prime-Time Nielsen Ratings | accessdate = 2020-10-08 | newspaper = Associated Press Archive | url = https://iw.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F8A2460CB05F5D4&f=basic | date = 1999-11-16}}</ref>。节目的[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森家庭收视比率]]为10.1/14，代表所有装有电视的家庭中有10.1%观看本集，同时所有当时在看电视的观众则有14%选择《第六次大灭绝：命运之爱》<ref name="Shapiro-2000" />{{rp|281}}。节目在英国共有84万观众收看，在天空第一台该周所有节目中排第三，仅次于《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》和《[[老友记|老友记]]》<ref name="barb2">{{cite web | url = https://www.barb.co.uk/viewing-data/weekly-top-10/ | title = BARB's multichannel top 10 programmes | publisher = [[廣播受眾研究會|Broadcasters' Audience Research Board]] | accessdate = 2020-10-08}}说明：需在右侧从上至下依次选择“2000”年、“{{lang|en|March}}”（三月）、“20 {{lang|en|Mar}} - 26 {{lang|en|Mar}}”（3月20至26日），左侧选择[[天空第一台|Sky 1]]后点“{{lang|en|View figures}}”按钮。</ref>。2003年5月13日，本集与第七季其他分集共同发布{{lang|en|DVD}}套装<ref>{{cite AV media | people = Kim Manners | year = 2006 | title = The X-Files: The Complete Seventh Season | publisher = 20th Century Fox Home Entertainment | display-authors = etal | url = https://www.amazon.com/The-X-Files-Complete-Seventh-Season/dp/B000089RT0 | medium = DVD | accessdate = 2020-10-08}}</ref>。两年后，《第六次大灭绝：命运之爱》又与其他涉及外星人殖民的分集一起发布《[[X档案神话第三卷：殖民|X档案神话第三卷：殖民]]》收藏版{{lang|en|DVD}}<ref>{{cite AV media | people = Kim Manners | title = The X-Files Mythology, Volume 3 – Colonization | year = 2005 | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox Home Entertainment | display-authors = etal}}</ref>。

[[File:Chris_Carter_(July_2008).jpg|评论批判[[克里斯·卡特 (編劇)]]编剧的部分内容过于花哨，华而不实|150px|thumb|upright]]

评论界起初对本集看法不一，西尔伯对结局感到失望，称“本集巧妙地把超现实主义与高潮即将来临的期待感相结合，但到头来根本没搔到痒处，只会让人失望”<ref name="space" />。在他看来，节目不过是“穆德经过可怕的磨难后花一周时间恢复”，处理太显轻巧，无法令人信服<ref name="space" />{{refn|《{{lang|en|X}}档案》[[X档案_(第八季)|第八季]]开局的《[[内_(X档案)|内]]》、《[[外_(X档案)|外]]》两集，以及第11集《[[天赋_(X档案)|天赋]]》的剧情表明，穆德遭遇的磨难已经导致脑损伤，造成无法手术治疗的脑疾<ref name="BBC1">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101010135853/http://www.bbc.co.uk/cult/xfiles/episodeguide/eight/page1.shtml | deadurl = yes | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/cult/xfiles/episodeguide/eight/page1.shtml | title = Within | work = BBC Cult | publisher = [[英国广播公司|BBC]] | accessdate = 2010-10-10 | archivedate = 2010-10-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Morgan | first = Jessica | title = Doggett, Part Deux | accessdate = 2013-02-13 | work = Television Without Pity | url = http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/show/the-xfiles/without-2.php | archive-date = 2013-02-03 | deadurl = yes | archive-url = https://archive.vn/20130203130024/http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/show/the-xfiles/without-2.php | publisher = [[NBC環球|NBCUniversal]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = The Gift | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100611023923/https://www.bbc.co.uk/cult/xfiles/episodeguide/eight/page11.shtml | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/cult/xfiles/episodeguide/eight/page11.shtml | work = BBC Cult | publisher = [[英国广播公司|BBC]] | accessdate = 2010-06-11 | archivedate = 2010-06-11}}</ref>。|group="注"}}。不过，他认可剧中穆德的梦境，认为人物陷入困境后体现的性格特点更加真实可信<ref name="space" />。《{{lang|en|X}}档案》研究员、独立评论员莎拉·史帝高对本集的评分为三星（最高五星），认为剧中的穆德不是烈士，而是受害者，所以体现出来的不是英雄特质，而是可怜<ref>{{cite web | last = Stegall | first = Sarah | title = Extinction or Extermination? | url = http://www.munchkyn.com/xf-rvws/6thextinction.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130824034458/http://www.munchkyn.com/xf-rvws/6thextinction.html | archivedate = 2013-08-24 | publisher = The Munchkyn Zone | accessdate = 2013-08-24 | year = 1999 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。汤姆·凯塞尼奇2002年著作给予节目好评，称赞“杜考夫尼创作的最后一幕美到极致，体现出穆德与斯嘉丽不断发展关系中蕴藏的美和力量”<ref name="Kessenich-2002">{{cite book | last = Kessenich | first = Tom | title = Examinations: An Unauthorized Look at Seasons 6–9 of the X-Files | publisher = Trafford Publishing | year = 2002 | isbn = 9781553698128 | accessdate = 2020-10-08 | url = https://archive.org/details/examinationsunau0000kess}}</ref>{{rp|218}}。在他看来，穆德的梦境“极具启发”，而且整集都值得仔细解读<ref name="Kessenich-2002" />{{rp|88}}。宝拉·维塔里斯在2000年10月的《[[神奇影院|神奇影院]]》杂志发文，对《第六次大灭绝：命运之爱》评分两星（最高四星）<ref name="cinepaula">{{cite journal | last = Vitaris | first = Paula | title = The X-Files Season Seven Episode Guide | journal = Cinefantastique | date = 2000-10 | volume = 32 | issue = 3 | pages = 18–37}}</ref>，批评剧中再度沿用“一人昏迷不醒，搭档四处寻找解药”的老掉牙剧情<ref name="cinepaula" />，但她觉得穆德的幻想情景美到赏心悦目<ref name="cinepaula" />。

随着时间的推移，评论界对本集看法渐趋肯定。[[罗伯特·希尔曼|罗伯特·希尔曼]]和[[拉尔斯·皮尔森|拉尔斯·皮尔森]]2009年著作《希望相信：{{lang|en|X}}档案批判指南，千禧年与孤胆枪手》给予节目四星好评（最高五星），称赞该集“以出色风格为第七季营造良好开端”，就像接力赛进入最后一棒时的群众欢呼般激动人心<ref name="shearman">{{cite book | year = 2009 | first1 = Robert | last1 = Shearman | first2 = Lars | last2 = Pearson | title = Wanting to Believe: A Critical Guide to The X-Files, Millennium & The Lone Gunmen | publisher = Mad Norwegian Press | isbn = 9780975944691 | pages = 207–208}}</ref>。两人赞扬剧中富于真情实感，包含大量神秘元素的电视剧往往很难做到<ref name="shearman" />。2012年，《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》刊登艾米丽·范德沃夫的文章，为本集打分“{{lang|en|B}}”（最高为“{{lang|en|A}}”），但批评卡特剧本“过于花哨”，是他在《[[祝福的赞美诗|祝福的赞美诗]]》营造辉煌后最华而不实的作品<ref name="avclub" />。她还批评剧中将杜考夫尼扮成老人的化妆“实在太穷形恶相”<ref name="avclub" />，但对本集和上集整体满意，觉得如果娱乐效果再强一点会更好<ref name="avclub" />。她特别称赞癌人看向窗外时显现的末日景像，觉得电视上能有如此精美的特技的确很了不起<ref name="avclub">{{cite web | last = VanDerWerff | first = Emily | title = 'The Sixth Extinction'/'The Sixth Extinction II: Amor Fati' {{!}} The X-Files/Millennium {{!}} TV Club | archivedate = 2019-11-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191116072826/https://tv.avclub.com/the-x-files-the-sixth-extinction-the-sixth-extinc-1798175161 | url = https://tv.avclub.com/the-x-files-the-sixth-extinction-the-sixth-extinc-1798175161 | work = [[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]] | publisher = [[洋葱报|The Onion]] | accessdate = 2020-10-08 | date = 2012-12-01}}</ref>。

部分评论在评选《{{lang|en|X}}档案》最佳分集时将《第六次大灭绝：命运之爱》入选。凯塞尼奇评选全剧最优秀的25集时把本集排在第13位<ref name="Kessenich-2002" />{{rp|218}}。[[极客巢穴|极客巢穴]]网站写手妮娜·索迪将本集与《生物起源》和《第六次大灭绝》组合成三部曲，在所有分集中排名第五，称赞这三集是《{{lang|en|X}}档案》不断发展的例证，看着剧情发展下穆德和斯嘉丽逐渐走向越来越全面而且无可逆转的失败境地，实在令人痛苦不已<ref>{{cite web | last = Sordi | first = Nina | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201006185343/https://www.denofgeek.com/tv/top-10-x-files-episodes/ | title = Top 10 X-Files episodes | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/tv/top-10-x-files-episodes/ | work = Den of Geek | publisher = Dennis Publishing | date = 2009-09-22 | accessdate = 2020-10-08 | archivedate = 2020-10-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[雪城邮报|雪城邮报]]》的马特·尚普林把《第六次大灭绝：命运之爱》排在全剧第九<ref>{{cite news | last = Champlin | first = Matt | title = CNY's Ultimate X-Phile Returns with Top Picks | publisher = [[先進出版公司|Advance Publications]] | date = 2002-05-19 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F3A270049816041&f=basic | accessdate = 2020-10-07 | newspaper = The Post-Standard}}</ref>。莫妮卡·库伯勒在《[[惊叹_(杂志)|惊叹]]》月刊发文，认为《生物起源》、《第六次大灭绝》和本集是《{{lang|en|X}}档案》殖民阶段杰作<ref name="exclaim">{{cite journal | last = Kuebler | first = Monica | title = The X-Files Colonization | journal = Exclaim! | publisher = Ian Danzig | date = 2005-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826000156/http://exclaim.ca/film/article/x-files_colonization-x-files | archivedate = 2018-08-26 | url = http://exclaim.ca/film/article/x-files_colonization-x-files | accessdate = 2020-10-08}}</ref>。《[[东湾时报|康特拉科斯塔时报]]》刊登迈克尔·利特克与乔治·阿瓦罗斯的评论，称本集结尾穆德和斯嘉丽虽未接吻，但却是剧中“极富柔情的瞬间”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Liedtke | first1 = Michael | title = 'X-Files' Finale a Tender One | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/10649FF000C4798F&f=basic | accessdate = 2020-10-08 | newspaper = Contra Costa Times | publisher = MediaNews Group | date = 2001-05-26 | last2 = Avalos | first2 = George}}</ref>。《娱乐周刊》也将这集结局列入电视上最优秀的34个“我爱你”桥段，声称观众看到这里都忍不住要起鸡皮疙瘩<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Gonzalez | first1 = Sandra | title = Mulder to Scully in 'The Sixth Extinction II: Amor Fati' on The X-Files | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | publisher = [[时代公司|Time Inc]] | date = 2019-05-20 | url = https://ew.com/gallery/25-great-tv-i-love-yous/?slide=341218#341218 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190413043431/https://ew.com/gallery/25-great-tv-i-love-yous/ | accessdate = 2020-10-08 | archivedate = 2019-04-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

